Package uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.util

Class IterableUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.koryphe.util.IterableUtil
  • public final class IterableUtil
extends Object
    An IterableUtil is a utility class providing capabilities for:
    • Lazily applying a Function, or a List of Functions, to each element of an Iterable
    • Flatmapping of nested Iterables via concatenation, to allow correct closing of the iterables
